Description_lang: $?a137011[When you gain or lose Tiger's Fury, your next single-target melee ability causes a Bloodseeker Vine to grow on the target for ${$s1/1000} sec.][Your Swiftmend causes a Symbiotic Bloom to grow on the target for ${$s2/1000} sec.]

description_blz.en_US: Your Swiftmend causes a Symbiotic Bloom to grow on the target for 6 sec.
description_blz.es_MX: Tu Alivio presto hace que crezca una Floración simbiótica en el objetivo durante 6 s.
description_blz.pt_BR: Sua Recomposição Rápida faz um Florescer Simbiótico crescer no alvo por 6 s.
description_blz.de_DE: Eure 'Rasche Heilung' belegt das Ziel für 6 Sek. mit 'Symbiotische Blüte'.
description_blz.en_GB: Your Swiftmend causes a Symbiotic Bloom to grow on the target for 6 sec.
description_blz.es_ES: Tu Alivio presto hace que crezca un florecimiento simbiótico en el objetivo durante 6 s.
description_blz.fr_FR: Votre Prompte guérison fait pousser Floraison symbiotique sur la cible pendant 6 s.

description_blz.ru_RU: Ваше "Быстрое восстановление" выращивает на цели цветок-симбионт на 6 сек.
description_blz.ko_KR: 신속한 치유 시전 시 대상에게 6초 동안 공생체 꽃을 자라나게 만듭니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 你的迅癒會使共生之花生長在目標身上，持續6秒。
